Ing '''kutsiliu''' (‘’knife’’ king Ingles) metung yang kasangkapan a bibilugan ning pulu o talanan a makatuglung king [[taram]] a gagamitan king pamangili. Iti metung yang [[kasangkapan]] a malyaring gamitan anting [[sandata]]. Minuna yang linto iti kanita pang [[w:Stone Age|adua ampong kapitnang miliung banua bayu ing panaun tamu]], at iti patunayan da reng kasangkapan a [[w:Oldowan|Oldowan]] .<ref>{{cite web | title = No. 1 The Knife - Forbes.com | url=http://www.forbes.com/personaltech/2005/08/31/technology-tools-knife_cx_de_0831knife.html?boxes=custom | accessdate = 2007-05-07 }}</ref><ref name="palomar.edu">{{cite web | title = Early Human Evolution: Early Human Culture | url=http://anthro.palomar.edu/homo/homo_3.htm | accessdate = 2007-05-07 }}</ref>

== Amlat ==
[[File:The knife Grinder - 1853.jpg|thumb|left|Ing Manais Kutsiliu (The Knife Grinder) - Ginulis neng by P. Weenix at dinukit (engraved) neng W. French - Mibulalag ya para kareng maki bandi kapamilata’nang AH Payne, Dresden & Leipzig - 1853 (''Ibat kareng Dr. Nuno Carvalho de Sousa Private Collections - Lisbon)]]

Melalang la reng [[Olduwan#Omo River basin|minunang kutsiliu]] kapamilata’ning [[w:knapping|knapping]] (papukpuk a pamagliluk [percussive flaking]) ning [[batu]], partikular deng mangasias a batu anti ing [[w:obsidian]] ampong [[flint]]. Kanitang kapanaunan a [Paleolithic]], mapalyaring ginawa yang kasangkapan a anti kanita ing [[Homo habilis]] ibat king [[dutung]], [[butul]] at aliwa pang materialis a gad masisira, dapot mewala no reti.<ref name="palomar.edu"/><ref>{{cite web | title = World's Oldest Stone Tools | url=http://www.archaeology.org/9703/newsbriefs/tools.html | accessdate = 2007-05-07 }}</ref>

Aniang panaun a [[w:Bronze Age|limang libung banua na ing milabas]], aniang sinulung ing pamanigobra at pamangamit kareng metal, bagya-bagya lang miyalilan [[tangsu]], [[bronsi]], [[bakal]], at banuang tauli, [[aseru]]. 

Gawa la kareng miyayaliwang materialis deng makabayung kutsiliu, kayabe no reng aserung samut a pangkasangkapan (alloy tool steels), [[w:carbon fiber]], [[w:Ceramic|losa]], ampong [[titanium]].

